ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectNo. 138 - (Nova Scotia) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER N° 138 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes the federal government to provide financial assistance to the province of NOVA SCOTIA with respect to the RAINSTORM that affected the region from December 12, 2010, to December 15, 2010.
